  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you can overwhelm the minds of those nearby. You can target one creature within 30 feet that you can see; that creature must succeed at a <em>Will</em> saving throw (DC = 10 + 1/2 your <em>sorcerer</em> level + your <em>Charisma</em> modifier) or it takes 1d6 points of damage + 1 point for every 2 <em>sorcerer</em> levels you possess and becomes <em>shaken</em> for 1 round. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your <em>Charisma</em> modifier.</p>"
